        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="LrYqxPvZOILsHqb8xlcf-27" parent="KyOj-fMh_73qf5zfZf-D-7" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;absoluteArcSize=1;arcSize=14;strokeWidth=2;align=left;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;verticalAlign=middle;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontSize=12;fontColor=default;" value="&lt;h5 style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11px; font-family: Verdana; white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Courier New&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;load_uk_grid()&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Verdana&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;font&gt;- Loads UK Grid shp file&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Verdana&quot;&gt;&lt;font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;- Ensure CRS (EPSG: 4326)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Verdana&quot;&gt;&lt;font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Verdana&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Returns &#39;df_uk_grid&#39;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-family: Verdana;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-family: Verdana;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 204, 0);&quot;&gt;GeoPandasDataFrame&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="124" width="526" x="53.5" y="394" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="KyOj-fMh_73qf5zfZf-D-8" parent="KyOj-fMh_73qf5zfZf-D-7" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;absoluteArcSize=1;arcSize=14;strokeWidth=2;align=left;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;verticalAlign=middle;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontSize=12;fontColor=default;" value="&lt;h5 style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11px; font-family: Verdana; white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Courier New&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;uk_grid_data_pipeline(df_uk_grid, df_viirs)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Verdana&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;- Replicates the full UK grid for each day in the years present in df_viirs&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Verdana&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Verdana&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Returns &#39;df_daily_grid&#39;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-family: Verdana;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-family: Verdana;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 204, 0);&quot;&gt;GeoPandasDataFrame&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="124" width="499" x="82.5" y="524" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="KyOj-fMh_73qf5zfZf-D-9" parent="KyOj-fMh_73qf5zfZf-D-7" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;absoluteArcSize=1;arcSize=14;strokeWidth=2;align=left;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;verticalAlign=middle;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontSize=12;fontColor=default;" value="&lt;h5 style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Courier New&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;fwi_load_pipeline(...,df_daily_grid,df_uk_grid...)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Verdana&quot;&gt;- Get FWI data for each of the grids and days required&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Verdana&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;- If FWI already exists in drive, load .csv,&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Verdana&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;- Else request data via API call&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Verdana&quot;&gt;- For each (grid_id, date) get the max and avg FWI for the grid and store as a single FWI row per&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Verdana; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;(grid_id, date)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Verdana&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Returns &#39;df_fwi&#39;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-family: Verdana;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-family: Verdana;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 204, 0);&quot;&gt;DataFrame&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
